  "title": "AIRCON SERVICING TECHNICIAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Conduct general servicing for aircon systems</li><li>Conduct chemical overhaul for aircon systems</li><li>Diagnose,troubleshoot and repair aircon systems</li><li>Propose and upsell aircon services to customers</li><li>Perform site surveys and advise customers on installation details</li><li>Daily reporting and weekly reporting to direct manager</li><li>Any other tasks, when required by the immediate supervisor</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Customer facing, friendly and patient personality</li><li>Must be able to handle physical work due to job nature</li><li>Able to use simple mobile technology</li><li>Open to learning</li><li>Have handman work experience</li><li>Effective handling of fault / emergency repairs and customer complaints</li><li>Possess Class 3 License would be an added advantage</li></ul>",
